    InfinispanCodeGenerator, JVSTMCodeGenerator, MemCodeGenerator, OgmCodeGenerator

    public class IndexesCodeGenerator
extends TxIntrospectorCodeGenerator
    This code generator enhances the default generation by adding indexation to fields annotated to have that behavior. To do so, it:
    • Changes setters to update the index (and initializes the index tree if needed)
    • Adds a static method to allow an index search by the field
    Author:
    nmld
